  &lt;/div&gt; 
  &lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt; 
   &lt;p&gt;Spring Cloud for Amazon Web Services：&lt;a href=&quot;https://cloud.spring.io/spring-cloud-aws/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;https://cloud.spring.io/spring-cloud-aws/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
